menu "Magnetic Slide Switch Sensor Selection"

choice
    prompt "Select sensor type"
    default SENSOR_MAGNETOMETER
    help
        Choose the type of sensor for magnetic slide switch detection.

    config SENSOR_LINEAR_HALL
        bool "Linear Hall Sensor"
        help
            Use linear hall sensor for magnetic field detection.
            This sensor provides analog output proportional to magnetic field strength.

    config SENSOR_MAGNETOMETER
        bool "Magnetometer Sensor"
        help
            Use digital magnetometer sensor for magnetic field detection.
            Provides more precise magnetic field measurements with digital interface.

endchoice

choice
    prompt "Select magnetometer type"
    default SENSOR_BMM150
    depends on SENSOR_MAGNETOMETER
    help
        Choose the specific magnetometer sensor model when magnetometer is selected.

    config SENSOR_BMM150
        bool "BMM150 Magnetometer"
        help
            Bosch BMM150 3-axis magnetometer sensor with I2C interface.

    config SENSOR_QMC6309
        bool "QMC6309 Magnetometer" 
        help
            QST QMC6309 3-axis magnetometer sensor with I2C interface.

endchoice

endmenu
